org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.document.association.spi

Interface AssociationRow.AssociationRowAccessor<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - The store-specific type for representing association rows
    Enclosing class:
    AssociationRow<R>

    public static interface AssociationRow.AssociationRowAccessor<R>
    Contract for obtaining association tuple values from the store-specific representation of an association row. Columns not present in the association key will be retrieved via this contract.

    Implementations should be stateless and one single instance should be used to access all associations of a given datastore.
